Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\bord0\fax0.12\c&H3D464A&\frx4\fry0\move(1412.858,624.001,887.143,621.715,26,1944)}猫尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,记入这个表格里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,做的不是很好 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,萩生同学的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你想看响崇高的艺术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,主题是爱和痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是把这个概念放大到极限的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在最后的十分钟真亏你赶得上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小莲的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是独具匠心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹能拿刀子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只要和绷带一起绑在手上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要做到那种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我来喂你吧 小牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对我这种人你竟然如此关心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,迷你猫尾草 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太太太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我这个平时一直在添麻烦的人做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 很害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,二位真是像天使一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,莲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,响可不会做这种丢人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你把响当成什么了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果莲无论如何都要的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,说到夏令营我以为会是让学生做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么一说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有点可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,吃完饭之后就去入浴就寝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,今天请早点休息来消除疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是为了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要来枕头大战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,枕头大战是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在剩下最后一人为止用这个互相攻击的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用这么危险的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 会让老师生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那就稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}我滚滚滚滚滚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有怎么用过被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,平常是睡床的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand Power
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 花子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,缎带解不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,让我回想起在小云雀家过夜的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也能和小云雀一起睡 真是开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在夏令营的时候要把发卡放在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈是这样和我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才听你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还一起过夜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,响同学和莲同学也是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,难得不会经常一起过夜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然小时候经常会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,最近完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然早上经常会来叫我起床
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,关系真是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候不是经常一起过夜的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 有什么不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,响可不会忘记 那些日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要熄灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,已经很久没有这样和莲一起睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小云雀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我吵醒你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 你睡不着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在大家一起 很兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是不习惯被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,握着手睡怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,羊羊羊 猫尾！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快起来 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想悠哉地睡到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,通告幸福班级全员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟之内做好准备到正门集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,迟到的人屁股要挨踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,总之赶快换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,眼镜 眼镜 眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,莲你别谁回笼觉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,七个队伍全员到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,各位同学第一学期已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,除开一部分因病缺席的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大部分同学都参加了夏令营
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老师觉得非常高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\blur2\t(0,250,\blur0)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs90\t(0,3500,0.05,\fs30)\bord0\c&H858585&\pos(630,85)\frx20\fry0\org(620.571,100)}箱庭 捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,进行幸福实训「箱庭捉迷藏」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,箱庭？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,捉迷藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼由我和…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,猫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,猫尾草！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那么开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来抓你们了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,手还会伸长？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莫名其妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,莲同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,萩生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,完全走散了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,到底捉迷藏是什么回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福班级的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个箱庭捉迷藏是为积极参与的各位所准备的特别科目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,特别科目？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还没出事的各位请确认下包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,说来这里面到底放了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,花子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,小云雀…piu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好大声…piu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有空管我哦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是莲同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在找大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但不敌高温和日照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只能像个青虫一样在树木之间蠕动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,蠕动简直适合废柴的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,先去找个没人的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,去找一个既凉爽又适合睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不会被猫尾草和老师找到的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要去午睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,包裹突然被风刮走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,挂在了水车上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去取下来的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你也挂上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点不好受不过这情景我见过！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是江户时代的游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那大概不是游戏而是拷问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好像没发现我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个搞不好视野挺差的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在 走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我真没有迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有标记的卡片和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,香蕉和罐装面包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,500ml的矿泉水瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,手套 毛巾和望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还有餐布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还有捉迷藏的规则说明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30}还有笛子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别吹 要被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,场地是被高墙隔离的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么藏都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,同一房间的5人全部被抓住则宣告游戏结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,到游戏截止的正午为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,根据被抓住的人数和时间来评分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这个四叶草是我们的队伍标识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,排名靠前的队伍将在夏令营第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,入住套房并且可以吃到豪华山珍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吊车尾的队伍将独自露宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,并且食物自行解决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不要变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么响会在这种地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,莲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,完了 这下完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,睡在榻榻米上都睡不老实了还要露宿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小云雀 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只要在中午之前不被抓到就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很轻松的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你这迷之自信从哪儿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还有后续
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的木雕被放在了各处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,各自找到自己的木雕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,并成功汇合的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,会得到额外点数
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,找到木雕然后汇合…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这里迟早也会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有点担心牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和大家一起找木雕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,饿 走不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,说来今天没吃早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得有香蕉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Banana！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,总之这个先给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,香蕉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bana~na~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一根的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一人一半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,果然没戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也不太行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,星形标识的抓到一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这样效率太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而且视野又差
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,编队整齐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,选哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这边不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我又成包袱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请放下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼来抓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,莲同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为要挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不过总算是和瀑布说拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不想和云雀丘她们汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但为了胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,首先要找到莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,「愿我尝尽七苦八难」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}※ 战国名将山中幸盛（山中鹿之助）的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福班同学们本身就背负着不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要对这样的她们降下试炼有些于心不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但这也是为了让这些可悲的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,能够获得真正的幸福
